### 更新凭证
POST http://localhost:8080/api/credentials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "secretId": "{{secretId}}",
  "secretKey": "{{secretKey}}",
  "defaultRegion": "ap-guangzhou"
}

### 查询地域
GET http://localhost:8080/api/regions

### 查询可用区
GET http://localhost:8080/api/zones?region=ap-guangzhou

### 查询实例规格（含库存状态）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/instance-types?region=ap-guangzhou

### 查询镜像
GET http://localhost:8080/api/images?region=ap-guangzhou

### 价格试算
POST http://localhost:8080/api/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "ap-guangzhou",
  "zone": "ap-guangzhou-4",
  "instanceType": "S5.MEDIUM2",
  "imageId": "img-xxxxxxxx",
  "systemDiskGb": 50,
  "dataDiskGb": 0,
  "bandwidthMbps": 2,
  "bandwidthChargeType": "BANDWIDTH_POSTPAID_BY_HOUR",
  "instanceChargeType": "POSTPAID_BY_HOUR"
}

### 创建实例（首页立即购买）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/instances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "ap-guangzhou",
  "zone": "ap-guangzhou-4",
  "instanceType": "S5.MEDIUM2",
  "imageId": "img-xxxxxxxx",
  "instanceName": "demo-cvm",
  "systemDiskGb": 50,
  "dataDiskGb": 0,
  "bandwidthMbps": 2,
  "bandwidthChargeType": "BANDWIDTH_POSTPAID_BY_HOUR",
  "instanceChargeType": "POSTPAID_BY_HOUR",
  "password": "{{instancePassword}}"
}

### 查询实例列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/instances?region=ap-guangzhou&page=1&size=10

### 查询余额（真实数据）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing/balance

### 查询账单（真实数据）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/billing/bills?page=1&size=10&billingCycle=2026-02
